Clerics who take the Cold domain are resistent to even magical sources of cold.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Resist Cold Energy: The cleric gains 5/- resistance against cold attacks.

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>creeping cold (2), hypothermia (3), elemental shield (4), cone of cold (6), polar ray (9).</i>